CrossFit WOD:
Strength:
Paused Deadlifts
3-3-3-3-3
*Pause for 2sec at the knees (on the way up and on the way down)

Metcon:
5 Rounds for time:
10 Dual KB Snatch (#24/16,x2)
10-8-6-4-2 Burpee Box Jump Overs
15 Weighted Situps (#20/15 plate)

Weightlifting:
Part 1:
6-7 sets:
2 High Hang squat snatch
60-80%

Part 2:
Snatch Pull
Hang Squat Snatch
5 x 2+1  60%
5 x 1+1   70%
3 x 0+1  75-80%

Part 3:
Squat Clean
Front squat
5 x 2+1  65%
5 x 1+1 75-80%
3 x 1+1  85%

Part 4:
Dip & Drive
Split Jerk
4 x 1+2 70%
3 x 0+2 80%
